node.text: 6 months with Emmett 🖤 We are all still very obsessed over here with this little guy 😍 Such an easy, happy baby we love him so much 😩 Longest but shortest 6 months of my life adjusting to 3 kids but I think I finally got it😅 #6monthsold #whenyousmile #babyboy
